This is an invitation to join us on a tasting panel for Sunday Times Food in Randburg, Johannesburg. So, sharpen your taste buds and come hungry. Led by food editor Hilary Biller, it's a feast, it's fun and it's FREE. All tasters will go home with a copy of the latest Sunday Times Cookbook as a thank you.WHEN: Saturday February 18, from 10am-1pmINTERESTED? E-mail your contact details to moorep@timesmedia.co.za by February 15, and we will confirm your attendance.